ticle=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"Top-класса экипировку, Low-класса экипировку и заряды (соски)","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""}],"meta":[]},{"id":"row-9","title":"","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","cells":[{"value":"8 уровень","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"62","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"Top-класса экипировку, заряды (соски)","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""}],"meta":[]},{"id":"row-10","title":"","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","cells":[{"value":"9 уровень","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"70","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"Top-класса экипировку","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""}],"meta":[]}],"compact":true},{"id":"guide-item-5266-craft-interlude-block-3","type":"prose","title":"","paragraphs":["Каждый уважающий себя крафтер должен иметь все рецеты ресурсов в книге крафта. 1 уровня Вы можете выспойлить сами (список ниже), а вот остальные придется купить на рынке или найти спойлера."]},{"id":"guide-item-5266-craft-interlude-block-4","type":"list","title":"","style":"unordered","items":["Recipe: Coarse Bone Powder (100%) с Utuku Orc Archer [8 lvl], северней деревни гномов.","Recipe: Steel (100%) с Garum Werewolf [9 lvl], северней деревни гномов.","Recipe: Braided Hemp (100%) с Goblin Scout [8 lvl], восточней от дороги к Obelisk of Victory [Деревня людей]","Recipe: Cokes (100%) c Rakeclaw Imp Hunter [7 lvl], южное побережье недалеко от деревни [Деревня орков]","Recipe: Leather (100%) с Rakeclaw Imp Chieftain [10 lvl] в Immortal Plateau, Northern Region [Деревня орков]"]},{"id":"guide-item-5266-craft-interlude-block-5","type":"prose","title":"","paragraphs":["Начиная с грейда для крафта вам понадобятся кристаллы, короторые можно добыть, разломав вещь, перетащив ее на иконку в инвентаре Crystallize (Кристаллизация)."]},{"id":"guide-item-5266-craft-interlude-block-6","type":"table","title":"","columns":[{"key":"column-1","label":"Колонка 1","align":"","width":""},{"key":"column-2","label":"Колонка 2","align":"","width":""},{"key":"column-3","label":"Колонка 3","align":"","width":""}],"rows":[{"id":"row-1","title":"","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","cells":[{"value":"Уровень Crystallize","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"Необходимый уровень крафтера","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"Грейд вещи для кристализации","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""}],"meta":[]},{"id":"row-2","title":"","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","cells":[{"value":"1 уровень","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"20","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"Grade","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""}],"meta":[]},{"id":"row-3","title":"","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","cells":[{"value":"2 уровень","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"40","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"Grade","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""}],"meta":[]},{"id":"row-4","title":"","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","cells":[{"value":"3 уровень","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"52","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"Grade","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""}],"meta":[]},{"id":"row-5","title":"","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","cells":[{"value":"4 уровень","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"60","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"Grade","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""}],"meta":[]},{"id":"row-6","title":"","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","cells":[{"value":"5 уровень","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"70","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"Grade","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""}],"meta":[]}],"compact":true},{"id":"guide-item-5266-craft-interlude-block-7","type":"prose","title":"Торговля","paragraphs":["Все города и деревни в игре имеют налог, самый маленький 10% в Гиране (именно поэтому на многих сервах Гиран является торговой площадкой). Если замок захвачен, то действует дополнительный налог владельца замка. Налог владельца замка, можно узнать у любого стражника."]},{"id":"guide-item-5266-craft-interlude-block-8","type":"callout","title":"Торговля и расчет","tone":"info","text":"Торговля и расчет","items":["Торговля и расчет","Купите Sword of Revolution в магазине оружия","1 шт. Crystal: D-Grade = Sword of Revolution (1.750.000 ) / 2545 = 687,6","1 шт. Soulshot: D-grade = (1 шт. Crystal: D-Grade (688 ) + 3 шт. Soul Ore (750 )) / 156 = 9,2","1 шт. Blessed Spiritshot: D-Grade = (2 шт. Crystal: D-Grade (1.376 ) + 8 шт. Spirit Ore (3.200 )) / 100 = 45,76","Купите 2 шт. Elven Sword в магазине оружия, отправляйтесь в кузницу Гирана к Пушкину и дуальте у него мечи","1 шт. Crystal: C-Grade = (2 шт. Elven Sword (2.417.500 ) + 5.423 + 54 шт. Crystal: D-Grade (37.152 )) / 784 = 3137,8","1 шт. Soulshot: C-grade = (1 шт. Crystal: C-Grade (3.138 ) + 15 шт. Soul Ore (3.750 )) / 476 = 14,4","1 шт. Blessed Spiritshot: C-Grade = (2 шт. Crystal: C-Grade (6.276 ) + 30 шт. Spirit Ore (12.200 )) / 200 = 92,3"]},{"id":"guide-item-5266-craft-interlude-block-9","type":"prose","title":"Профессии","paragraphs":["Artisan (Ремесленник) [20 - 39 уровень] - Первая профессия","Warsmith (Кузнец) [40 - 75] - Вторая профессия","Maestro (Мастер) [76 - 80] - Третья профессия"]},{"id":"guide-item-5266-craft-interlude-block-10","type":"prose","title":"Тату","paragraphs":["Greater Dye of STR (Str+1 Con-1) (Улучшенная Краска СИЛ <СИЛ+1 ВЫН-1>)","Greater Dye of STR (Str+4 Con-4) (Улучшенная Краска СИЛ <СИЛ+4 ВЫН-4>)","Greater Dye of DEX (Dex+4 Con-4) (Улучшенная Краска ЛВК <ЛВК+4 ВЫН-4>)"]},{"id":"guide-item-5266-craft-interlude-block-11","type":"list","title":"Скиллы","style":"unordered","items":["Пассивные","Активные"]},{"id":"guide-item-5266-craft-interlude-block-12","type":"prose","title":"Пассивные","paragraphs":["1-2 профессия"]},{"id":"guide-item-5266-craft-interlude-block-13","type":"table","title":"","columns":[{"key":"column-1","label":"Колонка 1","align":"","width":""},{"key":"column-2","label":"Колонка 2","align":"","width":""},{"key":"column-3","label":"Колонка 3","align":"","width":""}],"rows":[{"id":"row-1","title":"","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","cells":[{"value":"","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-interlude","html":""},{"value":"Create Item","href":"/pages/article.html?article=archive-guide-item-5266-craft-in